{"id": "ce2db86aaf6ab0d5da72b8bdfdaeaa19213a2cd4003aed1a1a6006d1de3607bb", "item_id": "af31e56b05:0", "text": "Working with UDIMs in Blender is very straightforward."}
{"id": "f73a329ff03bd1833222c21656da88deebe1718efedf68cc427a32e45f710ff1", "item_id": "af31e56b05:1", "text": "If your textures use the Mari UDIM style and the filename is:"}
{"id": "f6ddd0fabef4f6d8daf8b2146cd2954cd3e7bd099b38839d4a9ce8619e9cc24e", "item_id": "af31e56b05:17", "text": "Diffuse.1001.tex"}
{"id": "3d8a8402b9f7b54bae6f5aa37074b1b3cb8173b12a6d70c1d25472d01d78a815", "item_id": "af31e56b05:3", "text": ", you need to set the"}
{"id": "e5e1e2b3b2ea6e5e3e3294eb36b6d7ff4a7cc8fb79e891e166361284569defa7", "item_id": "af31e56b05:14", "text": "Atlas Style"}
{"id": "dd2c2b24cafe4ce4ff075da61675acfd2166b9329868109331ef75fde16f3ffa", "item_id": "af31e56b05:5", "text": "to UDIM (Mari) and in the filename parameter, use"}
{"id": "5766853952bff5d739e8d333beedbd24f339ea2c38077a6611da90ca2bcacbd4", "item_id": "af31e56b05:19", "text": "Diffuse.<UDIM>.tex"}
{"id": "c21f9ccabe69b75f65093e33c3c9d8a4fbc1e3821d8ea91c7489b58ac4792164", "item_id": "af31e56b05:7", "text": "for the textures to load into their correct UDIMs."}
{"id": "303c71975870f191f23863869bcf645ac30c425858d1feba5d3dadbea26d8dd2", "item_id": "af31e56b05:8", "text": "Note : <UDIM> can be in either UPPER or lowercase <udim>"}
{"id": "bceeacc668934bc699c0f230b3809c91365c843556470744ce4bec190e59f864", "item_id": "af31e56b05:9", "text": "A Mari UDIM example for the first UV tile would be"}
{"id": "76f0227cadc9d1c75b897f233f204a0fceeb97b05508273726ea30bf75017a24", "item_id": "af31e56b05:11", "text": "where \"1001\" replaces <UDIM> in the texture filename."}
{"id": "8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e", "item_id": "af31e56b05:12", "text": "Value"}
{"id": "971b974235a86ca628dcc713d6e2e8d975206cc84c858720ce046c2dab72855a", "item_id": "af31e56b05:13", "text": "Filename"}
{"id": "1cac5ea5460e7817a8242aee809f78e4212886802c123875cfebd09b92fd3b72", "item_id": "af31e56b05:15", "text": "Use in path"}
{"id": "b59b72be37f30c7aa30ce458ed9284d6af6a7a180de2b0081d384d944017387b", "item_id": "af31e56b05:16", "text": "Alternative"}
{"id": "367f137ed5a73cd9244364f9b856e152825c7ee7b2bbadc11f5db692603f1a16", "item_id": "af31e56b05:18", "text": "UDIM (Mari)"}
{"id": "48df9bd963a323b70ba614c52fe6c8221ce77fe6979c2c340549101b0ebb6706", "item_id": "af31e56b05:20", "text": "Diffuse.<udim>.tex"}
{"id": "15b59e76278155abc323ab4140bf12c7bb3e8be412f47f2d34a0af9d4ba32fc9", "item_id": "af31e56b05:21", "text": "Diffuse.U1_V1.tex"}
{"id": "3fd9fa12c4e59043ab799b5a8939b960875f08684dd28e88755850acb1a9a2c8", "item_id": "af31e56b05:22", "text": "UV Tile Base-1 (Mudbox)"}
{"id": "445ee2fb3a98a516a9678f1b580f1f5249a89cce612f634efaf053cd9353f203", "item_id": "af31e56b05:23", "text": "Diffuse.<U>_<V>.tex"}
{"id": "ba142b5f68b605d89ae929980b73d5d5c3070e9aecc76b6872765a77381bb9d9", "item_id": "af31e56b05:24", "text": "Diffuse.u0_v0.tex"}
{"id": "b53a9ca4d4f8f84a9f03424e1b3b8ec69d0dbb1b422c2c0cef380375219b248c", "item_id": "af31e56b05:26", "text": "Diffuse.<u>_<v>.tex"}
{"id": "18b7dd47679254aa1893f403a6a37eea3d78a27f22c5ceda7830449614288fd5", "item_id": "af31e56b05:27", "text": "Please refer to the full"}
{"id": "9a98283faeb62ec895b5d9d55c85ac92a3056b50d0c9b1042adc88f53eef2e7c", "item_id": "af31e56b05:29", "text": "page for more information"}
